<task id="t_constructing_support_letter_sponsering_company">
  <title>Drafting a Support Letter for Sponsoring Company</title>
 <taskbody>
  <ol>
    <li>Use a word processor to format a letter template.</li>
    <li>Highlight history of company and service(s) they provide.</li>
    <li>Include impressive achievements, projects, and accolades of company.</li>
    <li>Introduce client and highlight their job duties.</li>
    <li>Include impressive achievements, projects, and accolades of client.</li>
    <li>Detail how client's experience matches the companies job requirements.</li>
    <li>Finalize  letter with proposed salary and range of proposed employment dates.</li>
  </ol>
 </taskbody>
</task>